decision_conditions: Features And Elements Of The Works
description: Demolition of Ravensfield House and Fenella Building, nos. 1 - 3 Burroughs Parade, no.3 Egerton Gardens and Erection of part 4, 6 and 7 storey block and freestanding 5 storey rotunda building over cleared site and existing car park comprising new public library (675 sqm), Arts and Creative Industries facility (4,450 sqm), Safer Neighbourhood Team Unit (70 sqm), community floorspace, retail floorspace (415 sqm), 384 x purpose built student accommodation units, 28 x C3 residential dwellings, provision of 15 x blue badge parking spaces and 3 x car club parking spaces and landscaping. The application is accompanied by an Environmental Statement (and an Environmental Statement Addendum).
